Code base for the MSc Software Development Individual Project, The Univeristy of Glasgow. 

LearningSpot is a Django web application for distance learning, intended for use in UK schools.

This is a Django project, therefore in order to run, the following steps are required. 


1. Install Python 3.7
2. Clone Git Repository: https://github.com/Jgilius/LearningSpot
3. Create Virtual Environment
4. Activate
5. Pip Install Django 3.2
6. Pip Install requirements, use requirements.txt
7. Migrate Database, python manage.py migrate